Subject: cio: DASD cannot be set online
References: BNC#563999
From: Gerald Schaefer <geraldsc@de.ibm.com>
Patch-mainline: 2.6.33-rc1
Git-commit: 52ef0608e3ee4a511725e443c4b572fece22b353

Symptom: On some versions of z/VM, setting a DASD online fails consistently
             with error message "A channel path group could not be
             established".
Problem: Some versions of z/VM provide pre-initialized Path-group IDs
             and do not accept changes initiated by Linux.
Solution: Recognized pre-initialized Path-group IDs and accept them if
             the state required by Linux equals the state provided by z/VM.
Acked-by: John Jolly <jjolly@suse.de>

